{"content": "<p><strong>Fractal Artist | Science Designer | Engineer</strong></p><p>Shades of gold is a new collection of fractals by Ununx revealed live in om Art Show Four today with the live curation of shades of gold #5. </p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Fractals are everywhere like a snowflake or branch. If you look at coastlines or soil that has been eroded by water, it is a fractal.\" Ununx</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/unnamed-67.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/unnamed-67.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/unnamed-67.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/unnamed-67.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/unnamed-67.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>The <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/frxctals\">shades of gold collection</a> is different from Ununx's previous collection titled FRXCTALS which explored a wider range of outputs.</p><blockquote>\"Flame fractals are a different class that are more related to set geometry. Flame fractals are made iteratively solving mathematical equations to get the results you want. There are a wide variety of shades.\" Ununx</blockquote><p>The creation of fractal art lies somewhere between the generative art minted via Art Blocks Curated and illustrations. <em>'You plan what you are going to do but the result might surprise you'</em> says Ununx. Collectors prize Art Blocks Curated for varied, high quality output because the artist cannot cull pieces from the final set. The flip side with generative art like Ununx creates, is that he gets to decide the best pieces. \"I get to plan, design and enter the parameters then play with the shading\" says Ununx.</p><p>With the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/shadesofgold\">Shades of Gold collection</a> there is an interplay between chaos and symmetry. The more chaotic artworks in the collection introduce more randomised shapes that would not normally be present in a typical fractal piece.</p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"I don't like telling people what to feel. Let it be open.\" Ununx</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/unnamed-69.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/unnamed-69.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/unnamed-69.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/unnamed-69.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/unnamed-69.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x950e68f203b7416308ee89d0a73b4f16bdb92f12/4\">shades of gold #3 by ununx</a></figcaption></figure><p>MintFace favorite in the shades of gold collection is #3 for its appearance of a pseudo horizon that draws in the energy from above and below.</p><p><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/67513701457526660616214259203837055192656712040025641497760761294313698099201\">Branching of Neuronal Dendrites</a> is featured in the <a href=\"https://www.mintedbook.com\">Minted Book</a> and the details in print are absolutely stunning.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/unnamed-175.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"896\" height=\"878\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/unnamed-175.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/unnamed-175.jpg 896w\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/67513701457526660616214259203837055192656712040025641497760761294313698099201\">Branching of Neuronal Dendrites by Ununx</a></figcaption></figure><p>You can view more of Ununx sold out FRXCTALS collection or pick up one of <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/shadesofgold\">shades of gold</a> before they are gone!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-23-at-10.44.55-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1269\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-23-at-10.44.55-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-23-at-10.44.55-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-23-at-10.44.55-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-23-at-10.44.55-AM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/frxctals\">FRXCTALS collection by Ununx</a></figcaption></figure><hr /><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">shades of gold #5 by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ununkx?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ununkx</a> revealed today in the 4th <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OM100m?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@OM100m</a> gallery show curated by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a>.<br /><br />the detail is absolutely stunning if you go to OpenSea and zoom in -- the artist has higher-res versions available for collectors too. take a look yourself!<a href=\"https://t.co/zj9BYaWfAh\">https://t.co/zj9BYaWfAh</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/x078a73SE1\">pic.twitter.com/x078a73SE1</a></p>&mdash; W E ʌ R Y (@TheWearyLuddite) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheWearyLuddite/status/1528486212775751681?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure>"}